---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 293
  - Title: Mânava-dharma-sâstra
    Location: II 144
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Spiritual Master
---
He who fills duly both ears with the Veda is to be considered (like
one’s) father and mother; him one should never injure.
